From within the Ark, Teletran 1&#39;s warning systems came on. 

&quot;Approaching unknown intruders detected.&quot; Teletran&#39;s voice chimed. 

Maxima appeared from a nearby panel to look up, gaze a moment as she 
pondered, then started towards Teletran, &quot;bring up a visual,&quot; she demanded.

The security cameras flicked about over the landscape, as one locked on the 
distant forms. 

She walked up & narrowed her optics at the sight. &quot;Zoom in,&quot;

As the visual didn&#39;t zoom in too much, but just enough for her to not really 
know who it was. 

&quot;Analysis?&quot;

&quot;Unknown,&quot; Teletran replied.

&quot;Defenses up,&quot; Maxima commanded. There was NO way no one would get through. 
The contents of the Ark were far too important to her. 

As she said that, Teletran accessed the central system, soon enough the 
weapons hummed as they came up to full power.  the cameras scanned the whole 
of the perimeter to detect any slight movement. 

